Package gov.ca.water.calgui.tech_service

In this package we have the technical services like error handling, file system etc.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAuditSvc
    This is the interface for processing all the Audit records like adding, delete etc.
    IDialogSvc
    Interface for common JOptionPane for simple dialogs with CalLite logo, centered on main frame
    IErrorHandlingSvc
    This is the interface for handling different type of error like validatione, business, system and also used for displaying the error messages.
    IFileSystemSvc
    This is the interface for File Handling like reading and saving.
    ThreeFunction<A,B,C,R>
    This is a functional Interface which takes three parameters and one return type.
